videos.description: Baylor QB Seth Russell takes the snap and rushes through Texas' defense downfield for a 50-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Russell blasts past Texas defense for 50-yard TD

videos.description: Texas QB Shane Buechele completes a pass to Armanti Foreman streaking down the sideline for a 40-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Buechele evens score for Texas with 40-yard TD

videos.description: Seth Russell pass intercepted P.J. Locke III return for no gain to the Bayl 37
videos.headline: Texas's defense comes up with interception

videos.description: Texas RB D'Onta Foreman rushes through Baylor's defensive line into open field easily scoring a 37-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Foreman runs up the middle for 37-yard TD

videos.description: Seth Russell pass complete to Ishmael Zamora for 20 yds for a TD
videos.headline: S. Russell pass,to I. Zamora for 20 yds for a TD

videos.description: Shane Buechele pass intercepted Ryan Reid return for no gain to the Bayl 24
videos.headline: S. Buechele pass intercepted, R. Reid return  for 0 yds

videos.description: BAYLOR Penalty, Offensive Holding (Blake Blackmar) to the Bayl 0 for a SAFETY
videos.headline: Baylor called for Holding in the endzone, results in a Safety

videos.description: D'Onta Foreman run for 9 yds for a TD
videos.headline: D. Foreman run for 9 yds for a TD

videos.description: Seth Russell connects with KD Cannon for 15 yard touchdown before halftime.
videos.headline: Baylor cuts into Texas' lead with 15-yard TD

videos.description: Terence Williams run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Bears RB gets a push from teammate to score 2-yard TD

videos.description: Baylor's QB Seth Russell clears a Texas defender to put the Bears in position for 24-yard FG, Texas trails Baylor 34-26.
videos.headline: Bears QB Russell hurdles Texas defender

videos.description: Texas cuts down Baylor's lead with a 7-yard TD making the score 34-32.
videos.headline: Longhorns TE stays inside lines for TD
Texas' under-pressure FG cements the win
